The paper is a tutorial on the basic principles of machine learning, which is a broad and interdisciplinary field that intersects with several subfields of computer science. However, based on the content of the paper, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is dedicated to the study of algorithms and models that enable computers to learn from data. The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural networks (cs.NE), which are all relevant to machine learning.
